13106/* Bit definition for Ethernet MAC Control Register register */
13107#define ETH_MACCR_CSTF_Pos (25U)
13108#define ETH_MACCR_CSTF_Msk (0x1UL << ETH_MACCR_CSTF_Pos)
13109#define ETH_MACCR_CSTF ETH_MACCR_CSTF_Msk /* CRC stripping for Type frames */
13110#define ETH_MACCR_WD_Pos (23U)
13111#define ETH_MACCR_WD_Msk (0x1UL << ETH_MACCR_WD_Pos)
13112#define ETH_MACCR_WD ETH_MACCR_WD_Msk /* Watchdog disable */
13113#define ETH_MACCR_JD_Pos (22U)
13114#define ETH_MACCR_JD_Msk (0x1UL << ETH_MACCR_JD_Pos)
13115#define ETH_MACCR_JD ETH_MACCR_JD_Msk /* Jabber disable */
13116#define ETH_MACCR_IFG_Pos (17U)
13117#define ETH_MACCR_IFG_Msk (0x7UL << ETH_MACCR_IFG_Pos)
13118#define ETH_MACCR_IFG ETH_MACCR_IFG_Msk /* Inter-frame gap */
13119#define ETH_MACCR_IFG_96Bit 0x00000000U /* Minimum IFG between frames during transmission is 96Bit */
13120#define ETH_MACCR_IFG_88Bit 0x00020000U /* Minimum IFG between frames during transmission is 88Bit */
13121#define ETH_MACCR_IFG_80Bit 0x00040000U /* Minimum IFG between frames during transmission is 80Bit */
13122#define ETH_MACCR_IFG_72Bit 0x00060000U /* Minimum IFG between frames during transmission is 72Bit */
13123#define ETH_MACCR_IFG_64Bit 0x00080000U /* Minimum IFG between frames during transmission is 64Bit */
13124#define ETH_MACCR_IFG_56Bit 0x000A0000U /* Minimum IFG between frames during transmission is 56Bit */
13125#define ETH_MACCR_IFG_48Bit 0x000C0000U /* Minimum IFG between frames during transmission is 48Bit */
13126#define ETH_MACCR_IFG_40Bit 0x000E0000U /* Minimum IFG between frames during transmission is 40Bit */
13127#define ETH_MACCR_CSD_Pos (16U)
13128#define ETH_MACCR_CSD_Msk (0x1UL << ETH_MACCR_CSD_Pos)
13129#define ETH_MACCR_CSD ETH_MACCR_CSD_Msk /* Carrier sense disable (during transmission) */
13130#define ETH_MACCR_FES_Pos (14U)
13131#define ETH_MACCR_FES_Msk (0x1UL << ETH_MACCR_FES_Pos)
13132#define ETH_MACCR_FES ETH_MACCR_FES_Msk /* Fast ethernet speed */
13133#define ETH_MACCR_ROD_Pos (13U)
13134#define ETH_MACCR_ROD_Msk (0x1UL << ETH_MACCR_ROD_Pos)
13135#define ETH_MACCR_ROD ETH_MACCR_ROD_Msk /* Receive own disable */
13136#define ETH_MACCR_LM_Pos (12U)
13137#define ETH_MACCR_LM_Msk (0x1UL << ETH_MACCR_LM_Pos)
13138#define ETH_MACCR_LM ETH_MACCR_LM_Msk /* loopback mode */
13139#define ETH_MACCR_DM_Pos (11U)
13140#define ETH_MACCR_DM_Msk (0x1UL << ETH_MACCR_DM_Pos)
13141#define ETH_MACCR_DM ETH_MACCR_DM_Msk /* Duplex mode */
13142#define ETH_MACCR_IPCO_Pos (10U)
13143#define ETH_MACCR_IPCO_Msk (0x1UL << ETH_MACCR_IPCO_Pos)
13144#define ETH_MACCR_IPCO ETH_MACCR_IPCO_Msk /* IP Checksum offload */
13145#define ETH_MACCR_RD_Pos (9U)
13146#define ETH_MACCR_RD_Msk (0x1UL << ETH_MACCR_RD_Pos)
13147#define ETH_MACCR_RD ETH_MACCR_RD_Msk /* Retry disable */
13148#define ETH_MACCR_APCS_Pos (7U)
13149#define ETH_MACCR_APCS_Msk (0x1UL << ETH_MACCR_APCS_Pos)
13150#define ETH_MACCR_APCS ETH_MACCR_APCS_Msk /* Automatic Pad/CRC stripping */
13151#define ETH_MACCR_BL_Pos (5U)
13152#define ETH_MACCR_BL_Msk (0x3UL << ETH_MACCR_BL_Pos)
13153#define ETH_MACCR_BL ETH_MACCR_BL_Msk /* Back-off limit: random integer number (r) of slot time delays before rescheduling
13154 a transmission attempt during retries after a collision: 0 =< r <2^k */
13155#define ETH_MACCR_BL_10 0x00000000U /* k = min (n, 10) */
13156#define ETH_MACCR_BL_8 0x00000020U /* k = min (n, 8) */
13157#define ETH_MACCR_BL_4 0x00000040U /* k = min (n, 4) */
13158#define ETH_MACCR_BL_1 0x00000060U /* k = min (n, 1) */
13159#define ETH_MACCR_DC_Pos (4U)
13160#define ETH_MACCR_DC_Msk (0x1UL << ETH_MACCR_DC_Pos)
13161#define ETH_MACCR_DC ETH_MACCR_DC_Msk /* Defferal check */
13162#define ETH_MACCR_TE_Pos (3U)
13163#define ETH_MACCR_TE_Msk (0x1UL << ETH_MACCR_TE_Pos)
13164#define ETH_MACCR_TE ETH_MACCR_TE_Msk /* Transmitter enable */
13165#define ETH_MACCR_RE_Pos (2U)
13166#define ETH_MACCR_RE_Msk (0x1UL << ETH_MACCR_RE_Pos)
13167#define ETH_MACCR_RE ETH_MACCR_RE_Msk /* Receiver enable */

13169/* Bit definition for Ethernet MAC Frame Filter Register */
13170#define ETH_MACFFR_RA_Pos (31U)
13171#define ETH_MACFFR_RA_Msk (0x1UL << ETH_MACFFR_RA_Pos)
13172#define ETH_MACFFR_RA ETH_MACFFR_RA_Msk /* Receive all */
13173#define ETH_MACFFR_HPF_Pos (10U)
13174#define ETH_MACFFR_HPF_Msk (0x1UL << ETH_MACFFR_HPF_Pos)
13175#define ETH_MACFFR_HPF ETH_MACFFR_HPF_Msk /* Hash or perfect filter */
13176#define ETH_MACFFR_SAF_Pos (9U)
13177#define ETH_MACFFR_SAF_Msk (0x1UL << ETH_MACFFR_SAF_Pos)
13178#define ETH_MACFFR_SAF ETH_MACFFR_SAF_Msk /* Source address filter enable */
13179#define ETH_MACFFR_SAIF_Pos (8U)
13180#define ETH_MACFFR_SAIF_Msk (0x1UL << ETH_MACFFR_SAIF_Pos)
13181#define ETH_MACFFR_SAIF ETH_MACFFR_SAIF_Msk /* SA inverse filtering */
13182#define ETH_MACFFR_PCF_Pos (6U)
13183#define ETH_MACFFR_PCF_Msk (0x3UL << ETH_MACFFR_PCF_Pos)
13184#define ETH_MACFFR_PCF ETH_MACFFR_PCF_Msk /* Pass control frames: 3 cases */
13185#define ETH_MACFFR_PCF_BlockAll_Pos (6U)
13186#define ETH_MACFFR_PCF_BlockAll_Msk (0x1UL << ETH_MACFFR_PCF_BlockAll_Pos)
13187#define ETH_MACFFR_PCF_BlockAll ETH_MACFFR_PCF_BlockAll_Msk /* MAC filters all control frames from reaching the application */
13188#define ETH_MACFFR_PCF_ForwardAll_Pos (7U)
13189#define ETH_MACFFR_PCF_ForwardAll_Msk (0x1UL << ETH_MACFFR_PCF_ForwardAll_Pos)
13190#define ETH_MACFFR_PCF_ForwardAll ETH_MACFFR_PCF_ForwardAll_Msk /* MAC forwards all control frames to application even if they fail the Address Filter */
13191#define ETH_MACFFR_PCF_ForwardPassedAddrFilter_Pos (6U)
13192#define ETH_MACFFR_PCF_ForwardPassedAddrFilter_Msk (0x3UL << ETH_MACFFR_PCF_ForwardPassedAddrFilter_Pos)
13193#define ETH_MACFFR_PCF_ForwardPassedAddrFilter ETH_MACFFR_PCF_ForwardPassedAddrFilter_Msk /* MAC forwards control frames that pass the Address Filter. */
13194#define ETH_MACFFR_BFD_Pos (5U)
13195#define ETH_MACFFR_BFD_Msk (0x1UL << ETH_MACFFR_BFD_Pos)
13196#define ETH_MACFFR_BFD ETH_MACFFR_BFD_Msk /* Broadcast frame disable */
13197#define ETH_MACFFR_PAM_Pos (4U)
13198#define ETH_MACFFR_PAM_Msk (0x1UL << ETH_MACFFR_PAM_Pos)
13199#define ETH_MACFFR_PAM ETH_MACFFR_PAM_Msk /* Pass all mutlicast */
13200#define ETH_MACFFR_DAIF_Pos (3U)
13201#define ETH_MACFFR_DAIF_Msk (0x1UL << ETH_MACFFR_DAIF_Pos)
13202#define ETH_MACFFR_DAIF ETH_MACFFR_DAIF_Msk /* DA Inverse filtering */
13203#define ETH_MACFFR_HM_Pos (2U)
13204#define ETH_MACFFR_HM_Msk (0x1UL << ETH_MACFFR_HM_Pos)
13205#define ETH_MACFFR_HM ETH_MACFFR_HM_Msk /* Hash multicast */
13206#define ETH_MACFFR_HU_Pos (1U)
13207#define ETH_MACFFR_HU_Msk (0x1UL << ETH_MACFFR_HU_Pos)
